metadata.name: Alpha Pepe
metadata.description:
"Pepe in West America'' is a meme-art collection in the novel Post-Pepography genre. This series is a meme-tribute to the groundbreaking series "Life in West America" by Roope Rainisto, which uses post-photography techniques to create stunning images of America. Post-Pepography takes this concept one step further by infusing Pepe into the art in a process of AI additive-prompting, blending and deconstruction in Midjourney V5.1. 

The result of this process creates unique 1/1 Photo-Pepographic images, each a meme of an original Rainisto piece. Every meme is meant to capture the essence of Pepe in America, his life and his struggle to fit into the fabric of society.
